name: Eva ads
info: Over and above the traditional methods are the more modern, feedback based methods including bulk email campaigns, targeted bqu SMS campaigns, and the establishment, launching and marketing via social networking accounts to reach the maximum possible audience. The combination of all these tools working in unison produces the singular cohesive result of effective communication. What EVA is saying is, “Don’t just Advertise, Communicate!!!” The effectiveness of EVA is based on the unified force of all these tools working together in concert, and the availability of feedback channels provided to the targeted market through bulk email and bulk SMS services.

name: E-mediaxa
info: Stay in touch with your customers, and prospects with E-mediaxa.
